{"tid":945423,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"［就黎辭職，同事對我越來越差］我太天真？","createTime":"2018-12-18T01:15:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-19T14:08:07.000Z","uid":110779,"like":2,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"bd548704301635caaeeb332828643441bed0e95f","tid":945423,"uid":110779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T01:15:45.000Z","msg":"早晨，是咁的，<br />\n話說我一直當Ａ係好同事+好朋友，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢對我一直都唔錯既，成日Ｒ我水吹，友善傾計，一齊ＬＵＮＣＨ之類，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只係久不久會因工作誤會／溝通誤會而發下脾氣，多數好快無事，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我當佢係好朋友，所以一早將我會辭職唔撈呢單野講比佢知，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢一開始知道時，表示唔捨得／唔開心，驚應付唔到我既工作等等。<br />\n<br />\n之後，佢開始話好擔心我走左佢會好辛苦，因為要做埋我果份，又話我把工作做得太好，到佢接手會好辛苦。（開始比說話我聽）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到現在，佢對我越來越差，我感覺到佢同我講野開始HEA我，但又要主動同我講野，即係好撚假果種，搞到我好唔舒服。我唔想咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，最多咪唔講野，又唔係一定要講野，但佢依加日日都用好假既態度語氣同我講野，包括工作上既野。<br />\n早兩日仲因為工作意見不合而吊柒我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：上頭比較喜歡我既意見，決定用我方法做，之後佢就吊柒我多撚事，佢想用番自己方法做。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 吊那星，上頭係佢唔在場既情況下問鳩我意見，我照俾，我唔知佢之前同上頭講過Ｄ咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，我無心搞到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實我出年先正式遞信走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n請問宜家既局面係咪即係「人未走，茶就涼」？<br />\n我不禁開始諗，佢以前一直以來對我果Ｄ都係假，對我好係因為覺得我會長做長期要對住我，所以先故意建立一個良好關係。或者佢一直有唔妥我但唔出聲＋表面上又同我好？　總之就好心寒。<br />\n好似一知道就黎唔洗對我喇／又要接手我Ｄ野，就西鳩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n＝　＝以前果Ｄ都係假<br />\n好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81fe50ca4b72cc61a3f56423c0e19766702f62a2","tid":945423,"uid":66719,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T01:28:10.000Z","msg":"體諒下d無能力既人，好鍾意將自己不足推落其他人身上<br />\n<br />\n同埋有利益衝突就唔洗諗有真心朋友"},{"pid":"565922a2913203d95aae6bb546d34ae7e69d74d4","tid":945423,"uid":63588,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T01:29:50.000Z","msg":"理得佢咁多 走咪走on99"},{"pid":"e03226894f620c400d388a9ca0f44573c662f3a6","tid":945423,"uid":119363,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T01:31:16.000Z","msg":"睇到當佢係朋友呢到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3de8cfceaf389ee694e7b9231f5c2d640b47119a","tid":945423,"uid":110779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"81fe50ca4b72cc61a3f56423c0e19766702f62a2","tid":945423,"uid":66719,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T01:28:10.000Z","msg":"體諒下d無能力既人，好鍾意將自己不足推落其他人身上<br />\n<br />\n同埋有利益衝突就唔洗諗有真心朋友"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T01:39:28.000Z","msg":"我以後會記住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n多謝你回覆我，我要Ｄ時間接受佢從來都唔係我朋友。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12c4262c361055de0bac3fc68087bbd9b41729b9","tid":945423,"uid":110779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"565922a2913203d95aae6bb546d34ae7e69d74d4","tid":945423,"uid":63588,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T01:29:50.000Z","msg":"理得佢咁多 走咪走on99"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T01:41:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 　知道<br />\n<br />\n唉　諗起仲要對偽佢到完場就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4977b77db3a297e354d19fd6004bdbacfe8e8a47","tid":945423,"uid":110779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e03226894f620c400d388a9ca0f44573c662f3a6","tid":945423,"uid":119363,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T01:31:16.000Z","msg":"睇到當佢係朋友呢到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T01:42:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好撚慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我ＯＮ９<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a36f95d34aa95245af8475fea163b93accbc41b","tid":945423,"uid":35143,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T01:53:29.000Z","msg":"女人返工真係好撚煩"},{"pid":"60b7f46e0136d6e16754f8662a999e7cad3e7752","tid":945423,"uid":119330,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T01:59:42.000Z","msg":"從來都唔會當工作上既同事係朋友<br />\n傾下計 吹下水 OK<br />\n但私人野一定唔會講多<br />\n尤其是想走人辭職<br />\n除非我係想借佢把口傳出去<br />\n否則一定唔會同人講<br />\n<br />\n出黎做野 一向都係識做人 重要過識做事<br />\n做事 會有幾難 教得多 做得多就可以<br />\n做人 唔係話人教 你就識 仲要講累積<br />\n<br />\n雖然我睇唔起擦鞋仔<br />\n但係擦鞋咁易 又唔見你做<br />\n<br />\n奉勸樓主一句<br />\n做人做事 都要防一手"},{"pid":"b9be5dd5a78c1899e4e81cc6c0c6380efa63e149","tid":945423,"uid":23786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60b7f46e0136d6e16754f8662a999e7cad3e7752","tid":945423,"uid":119330,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T01:59:42.000Z","msg":"從來都唔會當工作上既同事係朋友<br />\n傾下計 吹下水 OK<br />\n但私人野一定唔會講多<br />\n尤其是想走人辭職<br />\n除非我係想借佢把口傳出去<br />\n否則一定唔會同人講<br />\n<br />\n出黎做野 一向都係識做人 重要過識做事<br />\n做事 會有幾難 教得多 做得多就可以<br />\n做人 唔係話人教 你就識 仲要講累積<br />\n<br />\n雖然我睇唔起擦鞋仔<br />\n但係擦鞋咁易 又唔見你做<br />\n<br />\n奉勸樓主一句<br />\n做人做事 都要防一手"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T02:01:41.000Z","msg":"strongly agger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d4a69d89b7103053aaaf37e8b46d7ffcceeb623","tid":945423,"uid":22104,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T02:11:56.000Z","msg":"其實你好on9<br />\n未遞信千祈唔同人講辭職<br />\n如果有一日你唔想遲<br />\n條友幫你揚哂<br />\n盞自己攞黎煩"},{"pid":"74422316c5e7f132f1ce8c799209af6ce17b2e1e","tid":945423,"uid":147892,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"bd548704301635caaeeb332828643441bed0e95f","tid":945423,"uid":110779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T01:15:45.000Z","msg":"早晨，是咁的，<br />\n話說我一直當Ａ係好同事+好朋友，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢對我一直都唔錯既，成日Ｒ我水吹，友善傾計，一齊ＬＵＮＣＨ之類，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只係久不久會因工作誤會／溝通誤會而發下脾氣，多數好快無事，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我當佢係好朋友，所以一早將我會辭職唔撈呢單野講比佢知，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢一開始知道時，表示唔捨得／唔開心，驚應付唔到我既工作等等。<br />\n<br />\n之後，佢開始話好擔心我走左佢會好辛苦，因為要做埋我果份，又話我把工作做得太好，到佢接手會好辛苦。（開始比說話我聽）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到現在，佢對我越來越差，我感覺到佢同我講野開始HEA我，但又要主動同我講野，即係好撚假果種，搞到我好唔舒服。我唔想咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，最多咪唔講野，又唔係一定要講野，但佢依加日日都用好假既態度語氣同我講野，包括工作上既野。<br />\n早兩日仲因為工作意見不合而吊柒我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：上頭比較喜歡我既意見，決定用我方法做，之後佢就吊柒我多撚事，佢想用番自己方法做。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 吊那星，上頭係佢唔在場既情況下問鳩我意見，我照俾，我唔知佢之前同上頭講過Ｄ咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，我無心搞到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實我出年先正式遞信走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n請問宜家既局面係咪即係「人未走，茶就涼」？<br />\n我不禁開始諗，佢以前一直以來對我果Ｄ都係假，對我好係因為覺得我會長做長期要對住我，所以先故意建立一個良好關係。或者佢一直有唔妥我但唔出聲＋表面上又同我好？　總之就好心寒。<br />\n好似一知道就黎唔洗對我喇／又要接手我Ｄ野，就西鳩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n＝　＝以前果Ｄ都係假<br />\n好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T03:43:16.000Z","msg":"辭職走人最忌亂咁同人講<br />\n番工極少真朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算真係friend個d都唔好太早講/講之後去邊到做<br />\n費是麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最好就走左先同佢講 無手尾跟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09bbe78cd557abc2f49347be7336d2c05921a4dd","tid":945423,"uid":210161,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7a36f95d34aa95245af8475fea163b93accbc41b","tid":945423,"uid":35143,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T01:53:29.000Z","msg":"女人返工真係好撚煩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T03:49:02.000Z","msg":"返工都有男人帶頭搞小圈子<br />\n係咁問人私隱野"},{"pid":"2677e21c6b077ce42bd8e4f00e76ed884150c730","tid":945423,"uid":46192,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T03:50:18.000Z","msg":"人地表面上對你好好, 背後日日講鳩你是非"},{"pid":"e765abaff1ccd80253dcd7bf6358aba13ec0eb78","tid":945423,"uid":210161,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8d4a69d89b7103053aaaf37e8b46d7ffcceeb623","tid":945423,"uid":22104,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T02:11:56.000Z","msg":"其實你好on9<br />\n未遞信千祈唔同人講辭職<br />\n如果有一日你唔想遲<br />\n條友幫你